        Explicit constructor of a satellite orbit object.
        Parameters:
        nom - Name of the satellite.
        sat_n - Satellite number.
        y - Reference year of the elements.
        d - Reference day and fraction of days.
        m2term - First derivative of the mean motion.
        incl - Inclination of orbit.
        ra - Right ascension of the ascending node
        ecc - Eccentricity.
        anomaly - Mean anomaly.
        wp - Argument of perigee.
        motion - Mean motion.
        rev - Number of revolutions completed at epoch.
        m3 - Second derivative. Set to 0 if no available.
        drag - Drag term. Set to 0 if no available.
